  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK953">
<l>nakaiyīkai yiṉco likaḻāmai nāṉkum </l>
<l>vakaiyeṉpa vāymaik kuṭikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A cheerful countenance, liberality, pleasant words, and an unreviling disposition, these four are said to be the proper qualities of the truly high-born.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
